er.  Come join us!  Meet in the HC Food Bank Parking Lot on Thursday\'s at 3:30pm...Blessings</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p class=\"p2\" style=\"text-align: center;\">[button link=\"#http://orovillehopecenter.org/monthly-donation/\"] Monthly Donations[/button] [button link=\"#http://orovillehopecenter.org/one-time-donation/\"] One-Time Donation[/button][button link=\"# http://orovillehopecenter.org/cant-help-now-pdf/\" color=\"orange\"] S.H.A.R.E.S. Card[/button]</p>','Mary\'s Story','','inherit','open','open','','173-revision-v1','','','2014-10-26 00:16:00','2014-10-26 00:16:00','',173,'http://orovillehopecenter.org/173-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(210,2,'2014-10-26 02:57:04','2014-10-26 02:57:04','&nbsp;\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">  </span>I am a Vietnam Veteran and I have been homeless for 26 years.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">  </span>For about 5 years I have been receiving Survival Services with dedication, grace and compassion from the staff.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">  </span>As I developed a relationship with them, they would help me navigate all the many resources that are available to me.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">  </span>One such resource is a Veteran’s Housing Outreach.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">  </span>Through this program I am now in an apartment after 26 years!<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">  </span>The Hope Center helped with furnishings; they delivered!<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">  </span>My life has changed immeasurable.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">  </span>Words cannot express the deepness of my gratitude.</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Survival Services</em></p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">Meets the most basic/stabilizing needs such as; food, clothing, personal hygiene items, sleeping bags, furniture, collaborative services (i.e. shelter, counseling), prayer and spiritual guidance<span class=\"s1\">.</span></