d we have plans on getting married soon with the City Quest team officiating!</p>\n&nbsp;\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>City Quest</em></p>\n<p class=\"p2\">Where saints from different organizations gather to be the hands and feet of Jesus and reach-out to those who live in apartment complexes and other isolated conditions...we meet needs and minister to those who would not normally make it to the Center.  Come join us!  Meet in the HC Food Bank Parking Lot on Thursday\'s at 3:30pm...Blessings</p>\n&nbsp;\n\n<hr />\n\n&nbsp;\n<p class=\"p2\" style=\"text-align: center;\">[button link=\"#http://orovillehopecenter.org/monthly-donation/\"] Monthly Donations[/button] [button link=\"#http://orovillehopecenter.org/one-time-donation/\"] One-Time Donation[/button][button link=\"# http://orovillehopecenter.org/cant-help-now-pdf/\" color=\"orange\"] S.H.A.R.E.S. Card[/button]</p>\n<br></br>\n<hr />\n\n[box]God through the HC distributes food to over 30 organizations throughout our City and Butte County. Last year God through the HC distributed a total of 284,742 lbs of food to individuals, families and organizations in need.[/box]','Toba\'s Story','','inherit','open','open','','232-autosave-v1','','','2014-10-27 01:58:05','2014-10-27 01:58:05','',232,'http://orovillehopecenter.org/232-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(251,2,'2014-10-27 01:58:22','2014-10-27 01:58:22','<br></br>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">  I had been attending the Serenity Recovery Group at the Nazarene church still struggling with my addiction until I learned I was pregnant.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">  </span>A year after my son was born, the City Quest Ministry came to my apartment complex giving out food and prayer.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">  </span>After an accident I was in, I began to go to church with the City Quest team.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">  </span>My boyfriend and I are now attending church together and we have plans on getting married soon with the City Quest team officiating!</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>City Quest</em></p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">Where saints from different organizations gather to be the hands and feet of Jesus and reach-out to those who live in apartment complexes and other isolated conditions...we meet needs and minister to those who would not normally make it to the Center.  Come join us!  Meet in the HC Food Bank Parking Lot on Thursday\'s at 3:30pm...Blessings</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p class=\"p2\" style=\"text-align: center;\">[button link=\"http://orovillehopecenter.org/monthly-donation/\"] Monthly Donations[/button] [button link=\"http://orovillehopecenter.org/one-time-donation/\"] One-Time Donation[/button][button link=\"http://orovillehopecenter.org/cant-help-now-pdf/\" color=\"orange\"] S.H.A.R.E.S. Card[/button]</p>\r\n<br></br>\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n[box]God through the HC distributes food to over 30 organizations throughout our City and Butte County. Last year God through the HC distributed a total of 284,742 lbs of food to individuals, families and organizations in need.[/box]','Toba\'s Story','','inherit','open','open','','232-revision-v1','','','2014-10-27 01:58:22','2014-10-27 01:58:22','',232,'http://orovillehopecenter.org/232-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(252,2,'2014-10-28 03:58:10','2014-10-28 03:58:10','&nbsp;\n<p class=\"p1\">  I have lived between homes for about 30 years after I destroyed my family with addiction.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">  </span>I came to the Hope Center for the hot meals.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">  </span>One day as I was eating, I sat at a table with a couple younger men,<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">  </span>As I was listening to them talk, one of them asked me how old I was.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">  </span>I told him and he replied that his Dad was about my age and that he hadn’t seen him in about 30 years.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\"